GIMP Plug-In - LDT (Layer Duplicator Tool)
=====================

Copyright (C) 2012  RemyDev <remy.awm.dev@gmail.com>

LDT (Layer Duplicator Tool) is a Gimp's plugin that provides an easy way to automatically duplicate the layer and apply some transformations and visual effects, such as - rotate, scale, move, blur and others ....

Features added: 
* - Colorize filter 
* - Noise Spread 
* - Drop Shadow 
* - Animation Options 
* - Blend layer with FG or BG (for animation) 



To build and install it, just ...

	./configure
	make
	make install

 ... and it's there.



Happy GIMPing,
--RemyDev & Mitch!
